strings.Value: "Looks like Tartuccio wasn't here for the Stag Lord. I don't know what he is up to, but I know what I'll do when I catch that snotty little saucebox..."
"It's curious that he wasn't concerned about the bandits and their chief. Something's wrong here..."
"Whatever he's up to, we should stop him."
"That gnome is a slippery snake. But spineless sneaks rarely work for themselves. They always need someone to take orders from..."
